                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Cresson</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Lima</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-04-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 22, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Have been informed by minister for foreign affairs of Peru that Ecuadorian answer
                    proposing mutual excuses is not at all satisfactory to Peru and their proposals
                    to resume direct negotiations inadmissible. Warlike preparations continue
                    methodically in spite of negotiations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cresson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
